cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with depth estimation and camera pose estimation using RGB images and sparse depth input. 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper mentions the importance of depth estimation for autonomous vehicles. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper proposes an end-to-end learning algorithm for depth refinement and completion. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with autonomous systems and machine learning. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is a less likely category but still possible as the paper deals with 3D environment reconstruction.
